review: Really fun game to play with friends, as it says it is in deep alpha so dont expect no bugs or perfect optomization for your pc. Still a really good game recomend+.
This isn't one of my top CoD's. For starters its completely dead no one plays, P2P hosting, and that makes getting into a good game with good rego is hard.
Extremely Fun To Play And Its Free!!! Would Recomend To Anyone Who Likes FPS Games.
